      {
        "q": "Are there age and experience restrictions?",
        "a": "Yes, the driver must be at least 24 years old and have a minimum of 4 years driving experience."
      },
      {
        "q": "What is the deposit amount and when is it returned?",
        "a": "The deposit varies from 1 to 5 million UZS depending on the model. It is fully refunded after the car is returned without damage."
      },
      {
        "q": "Is there a daily mileage limit?",
        "a": "The standard daily limit is 300 km. For long-distance trips, our 'unlimited' package is available."
      },
      {
